fao-voisit-asr = VoisIT Speech Recognition
fao-voisit-asr-description =
    The app understands Faroese speech and, with the help of AI, attempts
    to transcribe the text onto the screen. The result is influenced by
    how clear the pronunciation is, the quality of the microphone, and
    the amount of background noise – attention to these factors is
    therefore important.
fao-voisit-asr-links-0 = VoisIT ASR (in Faroese)
fao-voisit-asr-links-1 = VoisIT
fao-voisit-asr-links-2 = VoisIT

fao-sprotin = Sprotin dictionaries
fao-sprotin-description = Online dictionary resources for Faroese
fao-sprotin-links-0 = Sprotin

fao-korp = Korp for Faroese
fao-korp-description = In Korp for Faroese you can search Faroese texts. The text corpus is grammatically annotated.
fao-korp-links-0 = Korp for Faroese

fao-fid = The Faroese Inflection Database
fao-fid-description = The Faroese Inflection Database is a website where you can search for Faroese words and see their inflection patterns. The inflection patterns on the Faroese Inflection Database are in many cases much more detailed than the inflection patterns on Sprotin.
fao-fid-links-0 = Faroese Inflections

fao-browser-asr = Speech Recognition for Browser (beta)
fao-browser-asr-description = Record directly from your browser, upload a sound file, or insert a link to get the speech recognition tool to transcribe what is being said.
fao-browser-asr-links-0 = Speech Recognition (beta)

fao-dictus-asr = Dictus Speech Recognition
fao-dictus-asr-description = This software can transcribe what you say on Windows computers. You can be working in, for example, Word, Outlook, or some website, and have the program type for you.
fao-dictus-asr-links-0 = Dictus ASR

fao-stavseting = Faroese Spelling Dictionary
fao-stavseting-description = The Faroese spelling dictionary is authorized and establishes general Faroese spelling rules. It also has conjugation patterns for most of the words.
fao-stavseting-links-0 = Spelling Dictionary

fao-foenmt = Faroese-English Translator (Huggingface)
fao-foenmt-description = A machine translation model (FO-EN) that is being developed at the University of the Faroe Islands.
fao-foenmt-links-0 = Faroese-English Translator

fao-foen-ms-mt = Faroese Machine Translation (Bing)
fao-foen-ms-mt-description = A machine translation tool from Microsoft. It can translate both from Faroese and to Faroese.
fao-foen-ms-mt-links-0 = Translate to Faroese
fao-foen-ms-mt-links-1 = Translate from Faroese

fao-malradid = Word lists by Málráðið
fao-malradid-description = Search online dictionary resources for Faroese, by Málráðið
fao-malradid-links-0 = Málráðið lists

fao-online-speller = Faroese Online Spellchecker
fao-online-speller-description = Online spellchecker for Faroese: paste in your text and get checks.
fao-online-speller-links-0 = Faroese Online Speller

fao-googlemt = Google Machine translation for Faroese
fao-googlemt-description = Machine translation to and from Faroese, using Google.
fao-googlemt-links-0 = Google MT for Faroese
